# NOTE: assets/*.tflite is deliberately NOT ignored. EAS Build uploads only
# git-tracked files, and src/pose.js + src/useSwingCapture.js require() the
# model at bundle time — ignoring it makes every cloud build fail. It is a
# fixed 6.4 MB binary that never changes, so committing it costs nothing.

